# 3️⃣ FULL BALANCE MATH FORMULAS

We design from a baseline unit.

---

## BASELINE STATS

Define:
Base HP = 100
Base DPS = 10
Base Power = 100
Base Heat Tolerance = 100
Base Paradox Tolerance = 100

All modules scale relative to this.

---

# DAMAGE FORMULA

For each weapon:

Damage Output Per Shot:

```
FinalDamage = BaseDamage 
              × PowerEfficiency 
              × StabilityModifier 
              × TemporalModifier 
              × RandomVariance
```

---

## Power Efficiency

```
PowerEfficiency = (AvailablePower / RequiredPower)
```

Capped at 1.2x.

If below 1.0 → scaling penalty.

---

## Stability Modifier

```
StabilityModifier = 1 - (TorqueImbalance × 0.5)
```

TorqueImbalance = (WeightDifference / TotalWeight)

If imbalance > 0.4 → 20% accuracy loss.

---

## Heat Scaling

If quadrant heat > threshold:

```
OverheatPenalty = 1 - (ExcessHeat / MaxHeat)
```

Linear decay.

At 150% heat:
Module disabled.

---

## Paradox Scaling

Each second:

```
Paradox += Σ(ModuleParadoxRate)
```

If Paradox > 100:

```
OverloadChance = (Paradox - 100) × 0.02
```

Roll per second:
If success → random module disabled.

---

## Recoil Physics Approximation

RecoilForce = WeaponMass × ShotForce

Displacement:

```
Drift = RecoilForce / TotalMass
```

AccuracyPenalty:

```
AccuracyPenalty = Drift × 0.3
```

---

## Shield Formula

```
EffectiveHP = HP + ShieldValue × RechargeEfficiency
```

Reactive Armor:

```
BurstReduction = IncomingDamage × 0.3 (once per 3 sec)
```

---

# ECONOMIC SCALING FORMULA

Shop rarity odds shift by round:

Round 1–5:
Common 70%
Uncommon 25%
Rare 5%

Round 6–10:
Common 50%
Uncommon 30%
Rare 15%
Epic 5%

Round 11+:
Common 35%
Uncommon 30%
Rare 20%
Epic 10%
Legendary 5%

This prevents early snowballing.

---

# META SAFETY SYSTEM

To prevent “Steel Forger problem” (infinite scaling builds):

Implement:

Diminishing Return Formula:

```
StackModifier = 1 / (1 + 0.15 × (Stacks - 1))
```

Prevents exponential stacking.

---

# Final Design Philosophy

Depth comes from:

Placement × Physics × Heat × Paradox × Economy

Not raw stat inflation.

